# AUDIO::ENABLE_STALL_WARNING_SOUNDS

## Summary
Enable or disable the plane stall warning sounds

## Parameters
* **VEHICLE_INDEX** vehicle
* **BOOL** enable

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Works for planes only.
